<title>KTN::SessionCallback Class Reference</title>
<indexterm><primary>KTN::SessionCallback</primary></indexterm>
<para>

<para>The <link linkend="_class_k_t_n_1_1_session_callback">SessionCallback</link> class is an abstract base class that defines the interface for session callbacks. Session callbacks are used to handle various events and actions related to a trading session. </para>
 
</para>
